---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Custom Internal Platforms - intelio">
<main>
  <!-- HERO SECTION (Dark) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-black text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-normal mb-4 sm:mb-6">Custom Internal Platforms</h1>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-400">Purpose-built systems when off-the-shelf tools don't fit.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: When This Is Needed (Light) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-white text-black">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-normal mb-6 sm:mb-8">When This Is Needed</h2>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">Some organizations outgrow standard tools:</p>
      <ul class="space-y-4">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Too many disconnected systems</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Manual workarounds everywhere</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Critical workflows unsupported</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Competitive disadvantage due to execution limits</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: What We Do (Dark) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-black text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-normal mb-6 sm:mb-8">What We Do</h2>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">In select engagements, we design and build custom internal platforms.</p>
      <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">These may include:</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Internal operating systems</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Proprietary workflows</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Decision engines</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Advanced automation or intelligence layers</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">•</span>
          <span>Multi-department integrations</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-500 italic">Custom work is not default. It is evaluated based on impact, readiness, and complexity.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION: The Impact (Light) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-white text-black">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-normal mb-6 sm:mb-8">The Impact</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-4">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
          <span class="text-lg">Systems that fit the business—not the other way around</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
          <span class="text-lg">Reduced tool sprawl</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-700">
          <span class="text-gray-400 mt-1">•</span>
          <span class="text-lg">Sustainable execution advantage</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA SECTION (Dark) -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-black text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-normal mb-8 sm:mb-12">Have a complex problem that needs a custom solution?</h2>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-white text-black text-base sm:text-lg font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors min-h-[56px]">
        Work with Intelio
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
</Layout>

